Classifier: ChimeraX :: Bundle :: Structure Analysis,Visualization :: 1,1 :: ribxz_chimerax ::  :: 
Classifier: ChimeraX :: Command :: ribxz :: Structural Analysis :: Ribosome visualization tools
Classifier: ChimeraX :: Command :: ribxz loci :: Structural Analysis :: Visualize ribosome landmarks
Classifier: ChimeraX :: Command :: ribxz polymers :: Structural Analysis :: Apply ribosome coloring
Requires-Python: >=3.7
Requires-Dist: ChimeraX-Core~=1.0

This bundle allows users to fetch ribosome metadata from a remote server
    and automatically apply visualization settings based on that data.
    
    Commands:
    - ribxz loci: Visualize specific locations in ribosomes (tunnel, PTC, constriction sites)
    - ribxz polymers: Apply custom coloring to ribosome structures based on polymer types
